I could be interested in trading it for a more modern or surplus .32acp pistol..38 revolver, pump 12ga, marlin or ruger .22 rifle, silver bullion or ?????? make an offerI feel I must add, That this musket was found in the stairwell of a barn in Baton Rouge, La.
